▒▒│Funчуo    │Tk271Sit    │ Autor  │ Fernando Amorim    │ Data │ 26/01/10 │▒▒
▒▒│Funчуo    │Tk271Sit    │ Revisao│ Sonia Silva        │ Data │ 24/11/16 │▒▒
